INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("3308", "1", "2017-04-10 08:55:47", "2017-04-10 08:55:47", "[vc_row][vc_column][my_custom_shortcode text_attr=\"WHO WE ARE\"][vc_column_text]Over the last 10 years Enggsol has grown from being a specialist staffing solution provider in the IT and Engineering industry and expanded its services to the fields of accounting and finance, sales and marketing, human resource and administration, hospitality, telecommunications and logistics sectors. We however remain very loyal to our origin in the IT and Engineering domain and have a highly respected presence in the staffing industry.\r\n\r\nEnggsol has assisted clients to meet their business objectives by providing tailored staffing solutions and simultaneously have advanced the careers of many job seekers. We have established a fast, comprehensive and systematic process for recruitment that ensures that the interests and goals of all parties are met. We have a Talent Pool located throughout the Asia Pacific region and ensure our consultants adhere to the best search practices\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"3309\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]We have a strong focus on person-to-person networking and have developed personal links with some of the best people.Understanding the nature of our clients business, gathering requirements, and attracting high caliber candidates, is what we do best. Companies rely on us to find them high quality professionals for a range of roles in information technology, marketing, sales, accounting and finance.\r\n\r\nWe have grown in the last 10 years by delivering what we promise and we are often referred by clients and candidates simultaneously.Some of clients have been working with us from the day of our inception and we continue to ensure that the service level we extend to our clients is always at the best.\r\n\r\nWe are a company that is technologically innovative. We have traditional recruitment methods wrapped around technological innovation to ensure we are always ahead in finding the best talent for our clients.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"3237\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]", "WHO WE ARE", "", "publish", "closed", "closed", "", "who-we-are", "", "", "2017-04-11 07:50:06", "2017-04-11 07:50:06", "", "0", "http://localhost/enggsol/?page_id=3308", "0", "page", "", "0");
